    <rdfs:label>Semiology-motor-behavioral-arrest</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:comment>Interruption of ongoing motor activity or of ongoing behaviors with fixed gaze, without movement of the head or trunk (oro-alimentary and hand automatisms may continue).</rdfs:comment>
