  <hed:HedTag rdf:about="https://purl.org/hed/tag#Electrode-pops-artifact">
    <rdfs:label>Electrode-pops-artifact</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:comment>Are brief discharges with a very steep upslope and shallow fall that occur in all leads which include that electrode.</rdfs:comment>
