  <hed:HedTag rdf:about="https://purl.org/hed/tag#Eye-movement-horizontal-artifact">
    <rdfs:label>Eye-movement-horizontal-artifact</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:comment>Example for EEG: There is an upward deflection in the Fp2-F8 derivation, when the eyes move to the right side. In this case F8 becomes more positive and therefore. When the eyes move to the left, F7 becomes more positive and there is an upward deflection in the Fp1-F7 derivation.</rdfs:comment>
    <hed:hasHedParent rdf:resource="https://purl.org/hed/tag#Biological-artifact"/>
