    <rdfs:label>Screen-window</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:comment>A part of a computer screen that contains a display different from the rest of the screen. A window is a graphical control element consisting of a visual area containing some of the graphical user interface of the program it belongs to and is framed by a window decoration.</rdfs:comment>
