  <hed:HedTag rdf:about="https://purl.org/hed/tag#Time-sync">
    <rdfs:label>Time-sync</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:comment>A synchronization signal whose purpose to help synchronize different signals or processes. Often used to indicate a marker inserted into the recorded data to allow post hoc synchronization of concurrently recorded data streams.</rdfs:comment>
